text: Renan Abner do Carmo de Oliveira, known as Renan (born 8 May 1997) is a Brazilian footballer who plays as a forward for Gil Vicente. ==Club career== He made his Ukrainian Premier League debut for Lviv on 30 July 2019 in a game against Desna Chernihiv. ==References== ==External links== * * Renan Oliveira at ZeroZero Category:1997 births Category:Sportspeople from São Paulo Category:Living people Category:Brazilian footballers Category:Brazilian expatriate footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:FC ViOn Zlaté Moravce players Category:São Bernardo Futebol Clube players Category:Mosta F.C. players Category:San Gwann F.C. players Category:FC Lviv players Category:Gil Vicente F.C. players Category:Slovak Super Liga players Category:Maltese Premier League players Category:Ukrainian Premier League players Category:Primeira Liga players Category:Expatriate footballers in Slovakia Category:Brazilian expatriate sportspeople in Slovakia Category:Expatriate footballers in Malta Category:Brazilian expatriate sportspeople in Malta Category:Expatriate footballers in Ukraine Category:Brazilian expatriate sportspeople in Ukraine Category:Expatriate footballers in Portugal Category:Brazilian expatriate sportspeople in Portugal
